    Class and Description
    ExperimentConcurrentAccessException
    Exception class that signals a unique resource access has been attempted by more than one caller at the same time and that the invoker should try again in a short time

    Exception class that indicates an experiment or an experiment case could not be created
    ExperimentDataManipulationException
    Exception class that indicates some experiment data could not be stored, retrieved, or transferred

    Exception class that indicates there was an attempt to create a duplicate experiment, experiment case or item in a store
    ExperimentExecutionException
    Exception class that indicates there was a problem executing an experiment or an experiment case, or an action relating to those
    ExperimentNotCompletedException
    Exception class that indicates a requested operation cannot be performed because the associated experiment or experiment case has execution has not completed
    ExperimentQueryException
    Exception class that indicates a query for experiment information could not be performed
